{"about_the_game":"Eternights is a unique blend of dating and action where players can explore a post-apocalyptic world filled with danger, love, and adventure.<br> <br>Save the world, and find love along the way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Face the infected</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402110/extras/Eternights_Combat_GIF.gif?t=1727257807\" /><br>One day, something, or someone, has turned humans into dangerous monsters. All that interests them now is violence and power. They are what stand between you, a cure, and the world you want. Most importantly? You\u2019re fighting for more than just your own survival \u2013 you are fighting for those you love.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Find Love</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402110/extras/Eternights_Dating_GIF.gif?t=1727257807\" /><br>The impending end of the world makes for a great conversation starter! When you\u2019re not exploring dungeons, you can choose to spend time growing closer to a cast of five quirky and loveable characters. Explore their stories and grow closer to them to unlock unique skills and spells you can use in battle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Race the Clock</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402110/extras/Eternights_Calendar_GIF.gif?t=1727257807\" /><br>Scavenging, dungeon crawling, dating\u2026there are just too many things to do in one day, and each area has a deadline! Will you grow closer to your confidant in order to deepen your relationship and unlock new skills? Will you scavenge the wasteland for supplies? Will you grow stronger by training with your companions? Or will you ignore all of that and go to the dungeon the first chance you get?  It\u2019s up to you, but remember, the clock is ticking.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore Dungeons</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402110/extras/Eternights_Dungeon_GIF.gif?t=1727257807\" /><br>These dangerous areas - known as the &quot;Wall&quot; - are filled with mystery and danger. As the deadline looms, you will have to quickly overcome traps, puzzles, and dancing minigames to make it through in time.  Luckily, you have your confidants by your side to help when things get scary.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Animated Cutscenes</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402110/extras/Eternights_Anime_GIF.gif?t=1727257807\" /><br>There are several fully 2D animated cutscenes that change depending on who you decide to date. Immerse yourself and truly connect with the characters you are spending time with.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Time Lord","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1402110/7a636fc14bfa9a5f167ee3e45347e7301c97cf36.jpg"},{"name":"Shelter Escape","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1402110/f6969ea31d96c613bbe48f98274e9c0d70daee32.jpg"},{"name":"The First Bond","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1402110/92578f925fb3bc84bd850ef38e2e8955a1123339.jpg"},{"name":"Novice Scavenger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1402110/987d12b655ee743fb90b7822ff356da71d474b05.jpg"},{"name":"Master Craftsman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1402110/cd0b040f2c8c1931b22f154a9ae1140ba6045e91.jpg"},{"name":"First wall","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1402110/9508efbdc342c8eb9619c01e28ba9f450eea5b64.jpg"},{"name":"Piggyback Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1402110/2c7207655c3e7faa74112170321ce749dcd94419.jpg"},{"name":"Second wall","path":"http